<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>로그인 페이지</title>
    <link href="/css/loginform.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <body class="align">
      <div class="grid align__item">
        <div class="register">
          <img src="/img/logo.svg" />

          <h2 style="margin: 50px">LOG IN</h2>

          <form action="/loginresult" method="post" class="form">
            <div class="form__field">
              <input
                type="text"
                id="userId"
                name="userId"
                required
                placeholder="아이디"
              />
            </div>

            <div class="form__field">
              <input
                type="password"
                id="userPass"
                name="userPass"
                required
                placeholder="비밀번호"
              />
            </div>

            <div class="form__field">
              <input type="submit" value="로그인" />
            </div>
          </form>

          <p>아이디가 없으시다면 여기에서 <a href="/userjoin">회원가입!</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </body>
  </body>
</html>
